description: SECITS Holding AB engages in the provision of security information technology solutions. The firm offers camera surveillance, bank security, process monitoring, own modern operating hall for safe monitoring and own cloud service. The hardware for monitoring systems are standard products from such suppliers as AXIS, Bosch and Hewlett-Packard. The Company’s customers comprise banks, process industries, as well as chain stores operating in a number of market segments. The firm operates through Pronubecon AB, SECITS Sweden AB and MKS Sverige AB, among others. Its main shareholders are Pavi IT i Kramfors AB, Bjassbodarna Invest AB and Talien Invest AB. The firm operates domestically.
naics: Computer Systems Design and Related Services
name: SECITS Holding AB
